E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>老君曰：大道无形，生育天地；大道无情，运行日月；大道无名，长养万物；吾不知其名，强名曰道。夫道者：有清有浊，有动有静；天清地浊，天动地静；男</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>性功</category><category>早晚课</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>